x10.matrix.blas

Class DenseMultBLAS

  • x10.lang.Object
    • x10.matrix.blas.DenseMultBLAS

  • public class DenseMultBLAS
extends x10.lang.Object
    This class provides static methods to perform dense matrix multiplication using BLAS driver. The general case of matrix multiplication requires two input dense matrices, A and B, and one output matrix C. If plus = true, then performs C += A x B, otherwise C = A x B

multiplication using BLAS driver.

The general case of matrix multiplication requires two input
dense matrices, A and B, and one output matrix C.

If plus = true, then performs C += A x B, otherwise C = A x B
